extends ../templates/landingPage.pug

block head
	style.
		.testerActionButtons{display:none}
		.card-body.row .col-sm-2 {display:none}
		.text-muted{color:#5b6167 !important;}
		form{margin-left:30px; margin-bottom:50px}

block title
	|Sample page to test in WAVE - No issues

block breadCrumbs
	+breadcrumbWave
		|Sample test page to test in WAVE - No issues

block intro
	p.
		This a test page
	p.
		#[strong Note:] All known accessibility issues have been fixed and this page should produce a "clean" WAVE report.

 

block content
	.row
		.col
			h2
				img(src="../assets/images/Lotus_Flower_text.png" style="margin-top:20px" alt="Lotus Flower Information")
			p
				img(src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/Sacred_lotus_Nelumbo_nucifera.jpg/256px-Sacred_lotus_Nelumbo_nucifera.jpg" style="float:left; margin-right:20px; width:160px" alt="")
				.
					Nelumbo nucifera, also known as Indian lotus, sacred lotus, bean of India, Egyptian bean or simply lotus, is one of two extant species of aquatic plant in the family Nelumbonaceae. The Linnaean binomial Nelumbo nucifera Gaertn. is the currently recognized name for this species, which has been classified under the former names, Nelumbium speciosum Willd. and Nymphaea nelumbo, among others. (These names are obsolete synonyms and should be avoided in current works.) This plant is an aquatic perennial. Under favorable circumstances its seeds may remain viable for many years, with the oldest recorded lotus germination being from that of seeds 1,300 years old recovered from a dry lakebed in northeastern China.
	.row
		.col
			h3 Botany
			p The roots of lotus are planted in the soil of the pond or river bottom, while the leaves float on top of the water surface or are held well above it ...
			p
				a(href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nelumbo_nucifera#Botany") Read more #[span.sr-only about botany]
		.col
			h3 Cultivation
			p The Sacred Lotus grows in water up to 2.5 m (8 ft). The minimum water depth should not be lower than 30 cm (12 in). In colder climates such a low water level, which heats up more quickly . . .
			p
				a(href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nelumbo_nucifera#Cultivation") Read more #[span.sr-only about cultivation]
		.col
			h3 Use
			p Shows high potential for usage in wastewater treatment removing polluting compounds and heavy metals. It is able to grow in variable water conditions ...
			p
				a(href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nelumbo_nucifera#Use") Read more #[span.sr-only use]
	
	.row
		.col
			h2 Catalog
			p.sr-only
				img(src="../assets/images/lotusYogaPose.png" alt="Lotus Yoga pose")

			p Let us send you more information about lotus flowers.
			h3.h4 US Post
			form
				.row
					.col
						.form-group
							label(for="exampleInputFirstName") First name
							input.form-control#exampleInputFirstName(type="text" placeholder="First Name")
						
					.col
						.form-group
							label(for="exampleInputLastName") Last name
							input.form-control#exampleInputLastName(type="text" placeholder="Last Name")

				.row
					.col
						.form-group
							label(for="exampleInputAddress") Address
							input.form-control#exampleInputAddress(type="text" placeholder="Address" )
					
					.col
						.form-group
							label(for="exampleInputCity") City
							input.form-control#exampleInputCity(type="text" placeholder="City") 
				.row
					.col
						button.btn.btn-primary() Submit

			h3.h4 Electronic
			form.form-inline
				input.form-control.specialLabel#exampleInputSearch(type="text" placeholder="Email Address" aria-label="email" aria-describedBy="emailHelp")
				button.btn.btn-primary Submit

				p(style="width:100%")
					small.form-text.text-muted#emailHelp
							|Only enter 1 email address.

			h2 Social Media
			ul.list-inline
				li.list-inline-item
					a(href="http://facebook.com") 
						+faText("facebook-official", "fa-5x", "Facebook")

				li.list-inline-item
					a(href="https://www.snapchat.com/") 
						+faText("snapchat-square", "fa-5x", "Snapchat")
				li.list-inline-item
					a(href="http://twitter.com") 
						+faText("twitter-square", "fa-5x", "Twitter")
				li.list-inline-item
					a(href="https://www.instagram.com/") 
						+faText("instagram", "fa-5x", "Instagram")

			p(style="text-align:center")
				img(src="../assets/images/lotusBlossum.png" alt="End of page" style="width:70px")